 an \"effective resistivity\" are undermined by the\nnonlinearity of of the magnetic dynamics and the fact that the same turbulence\ndriving mass motion (traditionally identified as \"viscosity\") can alter\nmagnetic topology.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2009 20:18:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Oct 2009 22:33:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-02-11"}
