ation. The past Hubble sequence can be used\nto test these scenarios as well as to test evolution of fundamental planes for\nspirals and bulges.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jun 2009 21:06:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 22 Jun 2009 11:19:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2010 21:08:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-13"}
